Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dallas green book
des: The Dallas Green Book introduces users to Black Owned Business in the Dallas Fort Worth Area. Tell Alexa the type of business your are looking for and the Dallas Green Book will randomly select one from its database that fits your needs. Or, you can say "Tell me about the business XYZ", if you know the business name and Alexa will give you their description and telephone number. Details like its address or instagram will be sent to the Activities section of your Alexa app.
